</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<center>Gen. <a href="../Gideon_J._Pillow" title="Gideon J. Pillow" class="mw-redirect">Gideon J. Pillow</a><br />
<small>military recruiter under<br />
Bragg, then J.E. Johnston<sup id="cite_ref-114" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-114"><span>[</span>114<span>]</span></a></sup></small></center>
</div>
