<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Confederate_States_of_America&action=edit&section=47.php.html" title="Edit section: Military leaders">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Military_leaders">Military leaders</span></h2>
<div class="rellink boilerplate seealso">For more details on this topic, see <a href="General_officers_in_the_Confederate_States_Army" title="General officers in the Confederate States Army">General officers in the Confederate States Army</a>.</div>
<p>Military leaders of the Confederacy (with their state or country of birth and highest rank)<sup id="cite_ref-222" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-222"><span>[</span>222<span>]</span></a></sup> included:</p>
<div>
