<ul>
<li><a href="../Robert_E._Lee" title="Robert E. Lee">Robert E. Lee</a> (Virginia) – <a href="General-in-Chief" title="General-in-Chief">General-in-Chief</a> of the Armies of the Confederate States</li>
<li><a href="../P.G.T._Beauregard" title="P.G.T. Beauregard" class="mw-redirect">P.G.T. Beauregard</a> (Louisiana) – General</li>
