<li><a href="James_Longstreet" title="James Longstreet">James Longstreet</a> (South Carolina) – Lieutenant General</li>
<li><a href="Leonidas_Polk" title="Leonidas Polk">Leonidas Polk</a> (North Carolina) – Lieutenant General</li>
